    "The quantities are defined as follows: σ and γ are the thresholds of the sentence similarity and D is the dimension of the sentence representation.",
    "If the same word embedding type is input into different corpora, the parameters with the same physical significance are the same; if different word embedding types are input into the same corpus, the parameter settings are different.",
    "Therefore, when the input word embedding is word2vec, the parameters of the same physical significance of all corpora are different from Fasttext and Glove.",
    "Experimental ProcessWe fine-tune the parameters to minimize Eqs.",
    "16 and 17, consequently maximizing the Pcc and minimizing the MSE."
